BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (CHAPTER 3: CONFLICT RESOLUTION TOOLS) Tj ET
54 684.0 m 558 684.0 l 0.5 w S
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 658.2 Td (Healthy Conflict Is Normal and Necessary) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 630.4 Td (All couples argue. Research shows that 69% of conflicts in relationships are perpetual,) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 616.4 Td (meaning they never fully resolve because they are rooted in fundamental personality) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 602.4 Td (differences or values. The goal is not to eliminate conflict but to manage it in a way) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 588.4 Td (that strengthens rather than damages your relationship.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 564.6 Td (Healthy conflict means both partners feel safe to express their needs, differences are) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 550.6 Td (discussed with respect, and resolutions \(or compromises\) are reached that both partners) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 536.6 Td (can live with.) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 506.8 Td (The Softened Startup) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 479.0 Td (How you begin a conversation about a problem determines 96% of whether it will end well. A) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 465.0 Td (harsh startup \(criticism, blame, contempt\) guarantees a negative outcome. A softened) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 451.0 Td (startup dramatically increases the chance of productive dialogue.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 423.2 Td (Formula for a Softened Startup:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 407.2 Td (I feel _____________ \(emotion, not accusation\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 393.2 Td (about _____________ \(specific situation, not character\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 379.2 Td (and I need _____________ \(positive need, not criticism\)) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 351.4 Td (Examples:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 335.4 Td (HARSH: You never help with the dishes. You are so inconsiderate.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 321.4 Td (SOFT: I feel overwhelmed when the dishes pile up after dinner. I need us to find a system) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 307.4 Td (for sharing this task.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 283.6 Td (HARSH: You always spend money without telling me. You are irresponsible.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 269.6 Td (SOFT: I feel anxious when I see unexpected charges. I need us to have a quick check-in) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 255.6 Td (before purchases over $50.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 231.8 Td (HARSH: You care more about your phone than me.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 217.8 Td (SOFT: I feel disconnected when we are both on our phones during dinner. I would love to) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 203.8 Td (have device-free meals together.) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 174.0 Td (Practice: Write Your Own Softened Startups) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 146.2 Td (Issue 1: ________________________________________________________) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 132.2 Td (I feel ____________________________________________________________) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 118.2 Td (about ______________________________________________________________) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 104.2 Td (and I need __________________________________________________________) Tj ET
endstream
