BT /F2 12 Tf 54 370.8 Td (Repair Attempts) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 343.0 Td (Repair attempts are things you say or do during conflict to de-escalate tension.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 329.0 Td (Successful couples make repair attempts AND their partners accept them. Practice these:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 305.2 Td (- I am sorry. That came out wrong. Let me try again.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 291.2 Td (- I can see this is really important to you.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 277.2 Td (- You are making a good point. I had not thought of it that way.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 263.2 Td (- Can we start over? I do not like how this conversation is going.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 249.2 Td (- I love you. Even when we disagree, I am on your team.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 235.2 Td (- Let me make sure I understand what you are saying.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 221.2 Td (- I think we are both getting flooded. Can we take a break?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 207.2 Td (- What do you need from me right now?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 193.2 Td (- I appreciate you telling me how you feel.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 179.2 Td (- You are right about that part. I should not have done that.) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 149.4 Td (Conflict Patterns Awareness) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 121.6 Td (Track your conflicts for 4 weeks to identify patterns:) Tj ET
endstream
