BT /F2 12 Tf 54 714.0 Td (Apology Language Worksheet) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 686.2 Td (Different people receive apologies differently. Understanding your partner's apology) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 672.2 Td (language helps you repair effectively:) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 644.4 Td (The 5 Apology Languages:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 628.4 Td (- 1. Expressing regret: I am sorry. I feel terrible about this.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 614.4 Td (- 2. Accepting responsibility: I was wrong. There is no excuse.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 600.4 Td (- 3. Making restitution: What can I do to make this right?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 586.4 Td (- 4. Genuine repentance: I will change this behavior. Here is my plan.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 572.4 Td (- 5. Requesting forgiveness: Will you forgive me? I value our relationship.) Tj ET
