BT /F2 12 Tf 54 658.2 Td (The 5 Love Languages) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 630.4 Td (Dr. Gary Chapman's research shows that people give and receive love in five primary ways.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 616.4 Td (Understanding your partner's love language means you can express love in the way that) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 602.4 Td (actually makes them FEEL loved, rather than expressing it in the way that makes sense to) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 588.4 Td (you.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 560.6 Td (1. Words of Affirmation) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 544.6 Td (Verbal compliments, words of appreciation, encouragement, and hearing I love you. What to) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 530.6 Td (say: I am proud of you. You look amazing. I appreciate how hard you work for our family.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 516.6 Td (Thank you for always being there.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 488.8 Td (2. Quality Time) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 472.8 Td (Undivided attention, being fully present, shared activities, meaningful conversations.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 458.8 Td (What to do: Put the phone away. Make eye contact. Plan activities together. Have) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 444.8 Td (device-free meals.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 417.0 Td (3. Physical Touch) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 401.0 Td (Holding hands, hugs, kisses, cuddling, physical closeness, sexual intimacy. What to do:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 387.0 Td (Reach for their hand. Kiss hello and goodbye. Sit close. Give spontaneous hugs.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 359.2 Td (4. Acts of Service) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 343.2 Td (Doing things to make life easier: cooking, cleaning, running errands, taking care of tasks) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 329.2 Td (without being asked. What to do: Fill the car with gas. Make dinner. Handle a task they) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 315.2 Td (dislike.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 287.4 Td (5. Receiving Gifts) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 271.4 Td (Thoughtful presents, visual symbols of love, remembering special occasions, surprise) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 257.4 Td (tokens of affection. What to do: Pick up their favorite coffee. Remember anniversaries.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 243.4 Td (Give flowers randomly.) Tj ET
