54 684.0 m 558 684.0 l 0.5 w S
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 658.2 Td (Navigating Difficult Topics) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 630.4 Td (Every relationship has topics that feel scary to bring up: money, intimacy, in-laws,) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 616.4 Td (parenting differences, unmet needs, or personal boundaries. The longer you avoid these) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 602.4 Td (conversations, the bigger and more explosive they become. These scripts give you a) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 588.4 Td (starting framework for approaching tough topics with grace.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 564.6 Td (Remember: You do not have to resolve everything in one conversation. The goal of the first) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 550.6 Td (conversation is to be heard and to hear your partner. Solutions come in follow-up) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 536.6 Td (conversations after both people feel understood.) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 506.8 Td (Script 1: Talking About Money) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 479.0 Td (Opening: I would like to have an honest conversation about our finances. This is not about) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 465.0 Td (blaming anyone. I want us to be a team when it comes to money.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 441.2 Td (Questions to discuss together:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 427.2 Td (- What was money like in your family growing up?) Tj ET
