BT /F1 10 Tf 54 399.2 Td (- Are there spending habits either of us has that concern the other?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 385.2 Td (- What are our shared financial goals for this year? In 5 years?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 371.2 Td (- How should we handle individual vs. shared spending?) Tj ET
