BT /F1 10 Tf 54 261.8 Td (  Overall trust level: ___ / 10) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 238.0 Td (Partner 2 rates trust in Partner 1:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 224.0 Td (  Reliability: ___  Honesty: ___  Vulnerability: ___) Tj ET
